{"title":"Our governance","public_updated_at":"2014-08-09T11:47:46Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\">\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n<p>The Vehicle and Operator Services Agency (VOSA) closed on 31 March 2014. It has been replaced by the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/driver-and-vehicle-standards-agency/about/our-governance\">Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency</a> (DVSA). This is the information about VOSA that was published at the point that it closed. It is no longer current.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"boards-groups-and-committees\">Boards, groups and committees</h2>\n\n<p>Throughout the year, the chief executive and <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/policy-advisory-groups/vosa-directing-board\">directing board</a> have support from the following boards, groups and committees:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/policy-advisory-groups/vosa-investment-and-change-board\">investment and change board</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/policy-advisory-groups/vosa-business-performance-board\">business performance board</a></li>\n  <li>audit and risk committee</li>\n  <li>health and safety committee</li>\n  <li>remuneration committee</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","organisation":"f3dc9b48-1119-4130-9bc4-98f5e3fd7fab","tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/organisations/vehicle-and-operator-services-agency/about/our-governance","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"our_governance","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","first_published_at":"2016-05-13T16:11:36Z","base_path":"/government/organisations/vehicle-and-operator-services-agency/about/our-governance","description":"Our directing board which manages the agency, is made up of 7 executive directors and 2 non-executive directors.","content_id":"5f55d83e-7631-11e4-a